{"tid":754128,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[雖遠必誅] 十•一中國國慶  大埔區議會強推《戰狼2》當合家歡電影","createTime":"2018-07-24T07:15:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-01T03:34:26.000Z","uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b4ff2882d2edd2188984df1445f824cf8c98ac5b","tid":754128,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T07:15:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180705/large/1530785910_065d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180705%2Flarge%2F1530785910_065d.png&h=c38f5b0d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有唔夠3個月就係十‧一中國國慶，18區區議會當然又會大灑金錢，搞唔同慶祝活動盡顯愛國心。大埔區議會今日就開會討論慶祝十‧一活動嘅撥款申請，其中包括涉款約8萬元嘅社區電影欣賞。主辦機構雖然話係合家歡電影欣賞會，但播放嘅竟然係IIB級嘅《戰狼2》，雖然民主派喺會上力陳電影鼓吹暴力，但最終都喺建制派護航下通過咗。<br />\n<br />\n據知今日會上討論嘅包括喺6個社區會堂舉行電影欣賞會，建議播放電影有《戰狼2》、《黃金花》同埋《建國大業》。獨立民主派劉勇威同八方講，6個民主派議員都表明反對，因為《戰狼2》同《黃金花》都係IIB級嘅電影，當中有暴力鏡頭，唔適合喺社區中心做公眾播映，建議抽走項目，先討論其他。<br />\n<br />\n之不過咁，大埔區議會入面建制派佔大多數，雖然民主派議員力陳利害，但建制派都係照樣舉手通過，劉勇威擔心播放有關電影係主張暴力，又認為電影鼓動「雖遠必誅」，同建制派想要嘅國慶主題不合，大嘆建制派只係舉手機器，少少意見都唔肯聽。查實《戰狼2》同《建國大業》呢兩套戲，都係配合中國大國崛起嘅「愛國電影」，試問建制派又點會唔趁機，宣傳愛國思想吖！<br />\n<br />\n李八方<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180705/58404128\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180705%2F58404128&d=%2FrI7eD%2F6V29ZkNZAC5nNgAEk2Noh57F05xbgvjQdsX8%3D&h=e38677b2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180705%2F58404128&h=88836b47\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180705/58404128</a>"},{"pid":"81d685f20ac20b3332ec0552bede4919af6b216c","tid":754128,"uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T07:17:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://c.eazon.com/2013/12/1456607_557752460974198_86021471_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fc.eazon.com%2F2013%2F12%2F1456607_557752460974198_86021471_n.jpg&h=5a762964&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2eaa447af1237aa3fae7cc31dfceb5648171f848","tid":754128,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T10:00:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1f4b28d974821b2e92d3d6ce06eceebf8b542fb","tid":754128,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T03:34:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}